     C*****************************************************************
     C                     SETOF                     3032
     C                     Z-ADDA         CNO
     C                     Z-ADDYM        WKEYM
     C                     Z-ADDKE,M      WKEDD
      *
     C           FESGYO    IFEQ 0
     C           KE,M      ANDLED
     C                     SETON                     30
     C                     END
      *
